{"tid":541363,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"First they came...","createTime":"2018-01-26T10:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T18:05:52.000Z","uid":91083,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0092310e623761c4fbf8efab715ddaad490884de","tid":541363,"uid":91083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T10:45:05.000Z","msg":"起初他們DQ梁天琦，陳浩天；<br />\n梁家傑沒有出聲，<br />\n因為梁家傑反對港獨。<br />\n<br />\n接著他們DQ梁頌恆，游蕙禎；<br />\n梁家傑沒有出聲，<br />\n因為梁家傑想賺多兩個議席。<br />\n<br />\n然後他們衝向姚松炎和周庭；<br />\n梁家傑叫香港人俾D反應<br />\n因為DQ姚周「完全違反《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》保障人人無分種族、膚色、性別、語言、宗教、<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政見</span></span>等可享不受無理限制的選舉權。」<br />\n<br />\n到這時，已經沒有人願意替他說話了。"},{"pid":"5be4b5be62b14b92c146c9961a9248b9d3de1aad","tid":541363,"uid":35921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T12:17:37.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"f72f946d11e1ccbb5e3a3361c5523c525a707cd5","tid":541363,"uid":91083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5be4b5be62b14b92c146c9961a9248b9d3de1aad","tid":541363,"uid":35921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T12:17:37.000Z","msg":"幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T18:05:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}